The paper deals with the problem of navigation control of a general class of uncertain nonlinear multi-agent systems, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of Robotics (cs.RO), Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Learning (cs.LG). The proposed control protocol is decentralized, which implies that it could also belong to the sub-category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
